---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Us | Luxe Salon Dwarka"
	description="Learn the story behind Luxe Salon Dwarka — a premium hair, beauty and bridal studio built on trained expertise, premium products and a genuine love for the craft."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
<main>

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Luxe Salon Dwarka</span>
      <h1>Built by stylists, for people who take their appearance seriously.</h1>
      <p class="lede">What began as a two-chair studio in 2014 is now Dwarka's trusted address for hair, skin and bridal artistry — without losing the personal attention that started it all.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SALON STORY -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center;">
        <div class="hero-media reveal">
          <div class="frame" style="aspect-ratio:1/1;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633681926035-ec1ac984418a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Reception area of Luxe Salon Dwarka" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
          <svg class="part-line" viewBox="0 0 64 20"><path d="M2 16 Q 20 2, 32 10 T 62 6"/></svg>
          <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
          <h2>From a single chair to Dwarka's premium studio</h2>
          <p style="margin-top:18px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:16.5px;">Luxe Salon Dwarka opened in 2014 with one goal — bring salon standards usually reserved for South Delhi and Gurugram directly into Dwarka. Founder Simran Kaur, trained in London and Mumbai, started with a single chair and a strict rule: no service leaves the client without a proper consultation first.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:16px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:16.5px;">Twelve years on, that rule still holds. We've grown into a full studio spanning hair, skin, grooming and bridal artistry, but every appointment still opens with a conversation, not a price list.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION & VISION -->
  <section class="section tint">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <svg class="part-line" viewBox="0 0 64 20"><path d="M2 16 Q 20 2, 32 10 T 62 6"/></svg>
        <span class="eyebrow">Mission &amp; Vision</span>
        <h2>What we're building toward</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To deliver internationally trained hair, skin and bridal expertise to every client in Dwarka, with honest advice, premium products and zero upselling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m12 3-1.9 5.8L4 11l6.1 2.2L12 19l1.9-5.8L20 11l-6.1-2.2Z"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>To be the salon Dwarka families trust across generations — the first name that comes to mind for a haircut, a facial, or a daughter's bridal look.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR EXPERIENCE -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <svg class="part-line" viewBox="0 0 64 20"><path d="M2 16 Q 20 2, 32 10 T 62 6"/></svg>
        <span class="eyebrow">Our Experience</span>
        <h2>Over a decade of craft, measured in numbers</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal center-text">
          <h3 style="font-size:34px;">12+</h3>
          <p>Years serving Dwarka</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal center-text">
          <h3 style="font-size:34px;">9,400+</h3>
          <p>Clients styled to date</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal center-text">
          <h3 style="font-size:34px;">15</h3>
          <p>Trained specialists on staff</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal center-text">
          <h3 style="font-size:34px;">640+</h3>
          <p>Bridal looks completed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SALON ENVIRONMENT -->
  <section class="section tint">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="align-items:center;">
        <div class="reveal">
          <svg class="part-line" viewBox="0 0 64 20"><path d="M2 16 Q 20 2, 32 10 T 62 6"/></svg>
          <span class="eyebrow">Salon Environment</span>
          <h2>A calm, considered space to be worked on</h2>
          <p style="margin-top:18px;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:16.5px;">Spacious private stations, natural light, and a dedicated bridal suite mean your appointment feels unhurried — whether you're in for a 20-minute trim or a five-hour bridal package.</p>
          <ul style="margin-top:24px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:15px;"><svg style="width:18px;height:18px;stroke:var(--accent-dark);flex-shrink:0;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Private, air-conditioned styling stations</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:15px;"><svg style="width:18px;height:18px;stroke:var(--accent-dark);flex-shrink:0;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Dedicated bridal &amp; makeup suite</li>
            <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;color:var(--text-muted);font-size:15px;"><svg style="width:18px;height:18px;stroke:var(--accent-dark);flex-shrink:0;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>Complimentary refreshments during your visit</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-media reveal">
          <div class="frame" style="aspect-ratio:1/1;">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516975080664-ed2fc6a32937?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Interior view of Luxe Salon Dwarka styling floor" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY CLIENTS TRUST US -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <svg class="part-line" viewBox="0 0 64 20"><path d="M2 16 Q 20 2, 32 10 T 62 6"/></svg>
        <span class="eyebrow">Why Clients Trust Us</span>
        <h2>Consistency, honesty, and craft</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 15a7 7 0 1 0 0-14 7 7 0 0 0 0 14Z"/><path d="m9 11 2 2 4-4"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Certified Stylists</h3>
          <p>Every team member holds formal certification and completes annual technique refreshers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z" opacity="0"/><path d="M22 6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6z"/><path d="m22 6-10 7L2 6"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Transparent Pricing</h3>
          <p>Every quote is confirmed before your service starts — no surprises at the billing counter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Repeat Clientele</h3>
          <p>Over 70% of our monthly appointments are returning clients — the metric we're proudest of.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section tint">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-band reveal">
        <svg class="strands" viewBox="0 0 800 300" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0 250 Q 200 150 400 220 T 800 180" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M0 180 Q 200 260 400 150 T 800 260" stroke="#2DD4BF" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        <div class="cta-band-inner">
          <div>
            <h2>Come see why Dwarka keeps coming back.</h2>
            <p>Book a consultation with our team and experience the difference in person.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-actions">
            <a href="/contact#book" class="btn btn-primary">Book Appointment</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>


</Layout>
